    "description": "Error card headline: the attempted action requires the room to be open (a live session) before it can run. Imperative, instructional tone."
  },
  "errRoomNotOpenMessage": "This action needs a live room session on your daemon.",
  "@errRoomNotOpenMessage": {
    "description": "Error card explanation for acting on a room that is not open. 'Daemon' is a never-translate protocol/product term (the local background process, jeliyad)."
  },
  "errRoomNotOpenAction": "Open the room, wait for it to sync, then try again.",
  "@errRoomNotOpenAction": {
    "description": "Suggested next step when the room is not open: three sequential instructions the user performs in order."
  },
  "errNotAMemberTitle": "You're not an active member",
